1
00:00:06,768 --> 00:00:11,205
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,273 --> 00:00:14,800
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:14,876 --> 00:00:18,312
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,380 --> 00:00:21,975
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,050 --> 00:00:25,315
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,387 --> 00:00:27,321
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,124 --> 00:00:32,059
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,127 --> 00:00:35,927
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,331 --> 00:00:43,169
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,405 --> 00:00:50,470
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,779 --> 00:00:56,911
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,052 --> 00:01:01,318
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,389 --> 00:01:04,984
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,060 --> 00:01:08,393
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,463 --> 00:01:12,092
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,167 --> 00:01:15,762
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:15,837 --> 00:01:19,329
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,407 --> 00:01:22,865
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,078 --> 00:01:27,174
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:45,044 --> 00:01:47,740
<i>I'd like to prove that</i>
<i>I could become a splendid Ninja</i>

21
00:01:48,013 --> 00:01:51,244
<i>even though I can't</i>
<i>use Ninjutsu or Genjutsu!</i>

22
00:01:51,751 --> 00:01:53,548
<i>That would be the ultimate for me!</i>

23
00:02:20,246 --> 00:02:20,974
All right!

24
00:02:21,046 --> 00:02:22,980
I'm going to do my best again today!

25
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:26,508
Oh! Bushy Brow!

26
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:29,251
Oh... Good morning, Naruto.

27
00:02:29,321 --> 00:02:33,121
Hey, hey, did you already get checked out
by Old Lady Tsunade?

28
00:02:33,959 --> 00:02:35,187
How was it, how was it?

29
00:02:39,265 --> 00:02:42,860
The Leaf Village is
in great trouble right now,

30
00:02:43,135 --> 00:02:45,433
so we must do our best!

31
00:02:46,705 --> 00:02:47,899
You're right.

32
00:02:48,541 --> 00:02:50,133
Bushy Brow, you should get better
as soon as possible

33
00:02:50,209 --> 00:02:51,335
and succeed in your mis!

34
00:02:51,410 --> 00:02:53,105
- Naruto!
- Naruto!

35
00:02:53,846 --> 00:02:55,143
What's the matter?

36
00:02:55,848 --> 00:02:57,179
It's Konohamaru!

37
00:02:57,583 --> 00:02:59,414
Huh? What's wrong with Konohamaru?

38
00:02:59,819 --> 00:03:01,650
He's in trouble.

39
00:03:02,988 --> 00:03:04,148
In trouble?!

40
00:03:05,157 --> 00:03:11,027
<i>The Will of Fire Still Burns</i>

41
00:03:14,467 --> 00:03:17,368
At this rate,
we will have to open it by force.

42
00:03:17,703 --> 00:03:20,831
Try it! Who do you think I am?!

43
00:03:21,273 --> 00:03:23,264
I am the grandson of
the Third Hokage!

44
00:03:23,542 --> 00:03:25,373
If you go against me, then...

45
00:03:29,582 --> 00:03:32,210
It means you're going
against the Hokage!

46
00:03:32,785 --> 00:03:36,380
We need Lady Tsunade
to assume her position immediately.

47
00:03:50,269 --> 00:03:52,430
Those are Pepper Smoke Bombs!

48
00:03:52,838 --> 00:03:54,829
You'll get something even more terrible
if you come close to me.

49
00:03:55,274 --> 00:03:57,902
Honorable grandson! Even for you...

50
00:04:00,913 --> 00:04:03,575
There are things that can
and cannot be forgiven!

51
00:04:03,649 --> 00:04:04,616
Shut up!

52
00:04:08,053 --> 00:04:10,021
What is all this commotion
so early in the morning?

53
00:04:10,356 --> 00:04:12,187
It's hurting my head.

54
00:04:12,258 --> 00:04:13,225
Lady Tsunade...

55
00:04:18,464 --> 00:04:20,830
It's just one kid...
What're you doing?

56
00:04:21,033 --> 00:04:21,829
Yes...

57
00:04:22,568 --> 00:04:24,126
Get rid of him!

58
00:04:27,606 --> 00:04:30,700
But it's the grandson
of the Third Hokage!

59
00:04:30,776 --> 00:04:33,370
It doesn't matter if
he's the grandson or the great grandson.

60
00:04:33,445 --> 00:04:35,572
I am the granddaughter
of the First Hokage!

61
00:04:38,384 --> 00:04:41,512
He might just open his eyes
if he gets roughed up a little.

62
00:04:41,587 --> 00:04:42,849
Now move it!

63
00:04:43,188 --> 00:04:43,813
- Yes!
- Yes!

64
00:04:47,092 --> 00:04:48,559
Wait!

65
00:04:48,761 --> 00:04:49,659
Naruto?!

66
00:04:51,797 --> 00:04:53,662
Hey, hold on there.

67
00:04:53,933 --> 00:04:55,491
I don't really know
what's going on,

68
00:04:55,568 --> 00:04:59,629
but don't be so rough with Konohamaru,
Old Lady Tsunade.

69
00:04:59,872 --> 00:05:01,100
An acquaintance of yours?

70
00:05:01,874 --> 00:05:02,841
Yes, yes...

71
00:05:03,976 --> 00:05:08,037
I'll do the convincing,
leave it to me.

72
00:05:08,347 --> 00:05:10,440
Then, do something
by the end of the day!

73
00:05:12,451 --> 00:05:15,284
Oh, Lady Tsunade... Please wait!

74
00:05:23,462 --> 00:05:24,486
Excuse me.

75
00:05:24,763 --> 00:05:28,494
Oh, Sakura. Sasuke has already
been discharged from the hospital.

76
00:05:29,034 --> 00:05:32,492
I'm actually here to see Lee today.
Is he in the rehabilitation room?

77
00:05:34,807 --> 00:05:38,538
Not yet.
That's not like him to be late.

78
00:05:39,678 --> 00:05:40,838
I see.

79
00:05:47,553 --> 00:05:50,989
<i>The probability of a successful surgery</i>
<i>is 50%, at best.</i>

80
00:05:52,291 --> 00:05:54,122
<i>And if it fails, you'll die!</i>

81
00:06:03,435 --> 00:06:07,496
Hey, Konohamaru.
What are you doing in there?!

82
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:14,040
Hurry up and come out.
Then let's go eat some ramen.

83
00:06:18,417 --> 00:06:21,614
Don't worry. It's on me!

84
00:06:25,324 --> 00:06:27,792
You can have lots of BBQ pork, too!

85
00:06:30,629 --> 00:06:34,030
All right! You can have eggs too!
How about that!

86
00:06:36,402 --> 00:06:38,233
At least answer me!

87
00:06:38,303 --> 00:06:39,565
Shut up, you fool!

88
00:06:41,507 --> 00:06:43,907
You called me a fool!

89
00:06:43,976 --> 00:06:47,309
Open up already! I'll break in! Hey!

90
00:06:47,479 --> 00:06:49,447
Try if you can!

91
00:06:50,182 --> 00:06:53,379
W-Why you!

92
00:06:59,792 --> 00:07:01,521
- Naruto...
- Naruto!

93
00:07:10,002 --> 00:07:12,835
Oh, Lee... You're here.

94
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,198
S-Sakura!

95
00:07:17,876 --> 00:07:19,275
I wanted to bring you this.

96
00:07:23,782 --> 00:07:25,875
F-For... me?

97
00:07:27,052 --> 00:07:28,610
Th-Thank you very much!

98
00:07:31,557 --> 00:07:33,422
I-I'm sorry, Sakura.

99
00:07:33,792 --> 00:07:34,554
No worries.

100
00:07:36,095 --> 00:07:39,587
Sasuke is now recuperating at home.

101
00:07:39,998 --> 00:07:41,363
Thanks to Lady Tsunade.

102
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:42,758
At this rate,

103
00:07:42,835 --> 00:07:44,826
seems like he'll be able
to get back to his duties very soon.

104
00:07:45,904 --> 00:07:48,964
I see. That's very good.

105
00:07:49,808 --> 00:07:52,003
Lady Tsunade is great, after all.

106
00:07:52,711 --> 00:07:56,909
I think if you had her take a look,
you'd get better very quickly.

107
00:08:01,854 --> 00:08:02,582
Yes...

108
00:08:03,222 --> 00:08:06,350
But if there is something
that I can do,

109
00:08:06,425 --> 00:08:07,892
please feel free to tell me.

110
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:13,564
Thank you very much, Sakura.

111
00:08:14,867 --> 00:08:16,528
Then I'll see you soon.

112
00:08:29,382 --> 00:08:32,317
I would think that at least
one bar would be open.

113
00:08:32,718 --> 00:08:36,745
There's no way.
What time do you think it is right now?

114
00:08:37,156 --> 00:08:39,784
I can't drink sake, and I can't gamble.

115
00:08:40,126 --> 00:08:43,892
This place, the Hidden Leaf Village,
is no fun at all.

116
00:08:45,131 --> 00:08:46,428
Just like the Third Hokage.

117
00:08:46,499 --> 00:08:47,625
Lady Tsunade!

118
00:08:47,767 --> 00:08:50,167
Oh, I'm tired.

119
00:08:50,403 --> 00:08:54,567
I just want to sit down and
have a drink somewhere.

120
00:08:58,377 --> 00:08:59,503
I understand.

121
00:09:00,079 --> 00:09:03,810
I will take you to a place where
you can sit and have a drink.

122
00:09:04,216 --> 00:09:04,944
What?

123
00:09:06,419 --> 00:09:09,115
But I <i>will</i> have you do your work!

124
00:09:17,997 --> 00:09:21,433
Here now, go ahead. It's hot.

125
00:09:23,669 --> 00:09:28,106
Shizune... you've suddenly
become very strict!

126
00:09:28,708 --> 00:09:33,304
I haven't gotten strict.
It's probably that you were not aware.

127
00:09:34,113 --> 00:09:35,011
Not aware?!

128
00:09:35,514 --> 00:09:38,039
"If I can't get in the room,
then I don't have to work.

129
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:41,083
Isn't that what you were thinking?

130
00:09:41,554 --> 00:09:44,318
And that's why
you left it up to Naruto.

131
00:09:44,857 --> 00:09:46,791
Humph! Could be...

132
00:09:47,593 --> 00:09:50,323
This is the most recent list
of Ninja.

133
00:09:51,063 --> 00:09:54,396
The names and lineups of
the groups have changed a lot.

134
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,834
So please look through them.
And I mean, look through all of it!

135
00:10:00,473 --> 00:10:01,735
Oh bother.

136
00:10:02,241 --> 00:10:03,902
They have sweet rice cakes, too.

137
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:06,701
I don't like sweet things!

138
00:10:07,413 --> 00:10:11,008
Hey! Konohamaru, come out already!

139
00:10:12,785 --> 00:10:17,017
At least tell me why you're doing this!

140
00:10:17,957 --> 00:10:19,288
Konohamaru!

141
00:10:20,226 --> 00:10:21,022
Darn!

142
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:24,060
Everybody came here because
they're worried about you!

143
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:26,926
If you don't come out,
I'm going to drag you out of there!

144
00:10:27,366 --> 00:10:28,628
Naruto Sacred Technique...

145
00:10:28,934 --> 00:10:30,265
Sexy Jutsu!

146
00:10:33,305 --> 00:10:36,900
Konohamaru, come out!

147
00:10:39,445 --> 00:10:43,541
Konohamaru, hurry!

148
00:10:49,588 --> 00:10:55,254
Hey! Say something at least!
This is so embarrassing

149
00:10:56,195 --> 00:10:58,026
Don't fool around with me!

150
00:10:58,497 --> 00:11:00,021
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

151
00:11:01,901 --> 00:11:04,335
- Stop it already, Konohamaru!
- Stop it already, Konohamaru!

152
00:11:04,537 --> 00:11:06,004
One, two...

153
00:11:09,909 --> 00:11:12,776
- Uh, what is this?
- What the?!

154
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:16,377
What's going on?!

155
00:11:17,283 --> 00:11:19,376
Are you okay? Naruto?

156
00:11:22,755 --> 00:11:25,883
This is the Old Man's room.

157
00:11:34,689 --> 00:11:38,455
Eight D-rank missions,
three C-rank missions...

158
00:11:39,494 --> 00:11:41,689
I see, very much like the Kurenai team.

159
00:11:44,265 --> 00:11:47,325
We can easily figure out
what the Third Hokage was thinking.

160
00:11:51,372 --> 00:11:54,000
This is the same as
their parents team.

161
00:11:57,612 --> 00:11:58,670
I see.

162
00:11:59,981 --> 00:12:06,079
Oh, I see. This team has their own specialty
and is well balanced.

163
00:12:25,673 --> 00:12:26,799
My shoulders are stiff.

164
00:12:26,875 --> 00:12:28,809
I'm going to go get
some fresh air outside.

165
00:12:54,769 --> 00:12:55,758
Success...

166
00:13:01,042 --> 00:13:02,339
Success...

167
00:13:15,156 --> 00:13:16,316
Naruto...

168
00:13:16,524 --> 00:13:19,789
Uh... Darn!

169
00:13:20,128 --> 00:13:23,291
If that's how you're going to be,
then I'm not going to go easy on you.

170
00:13:23,398 --> 00:13:25,093
This is the Old Man's room!

171
00:13:25,233 --> 00:13:27,292
I won't let anybody
use this room besides him!

172
00:13:29,904 --> 00:13:31,269
The Old Man's...?

173
00:13:31,706 --> 00:13:34,300
That's why, as his grandson,
I'm going to protect it!

174
00:13:34,442 --> 00:13:36,876
Fool! This isn't the time for that!

175
00:13:37,045 --> 00:13:39,343
The Leaf Village is in great danger!

176
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:42,472
So what?! It doesn't matter to me.

177
00:13:43,451 --> 00:13:45,180
Are you seriously saying that?!

178
00:13:47,755 --> 00:13:50,019
Oh, now I'm mad!

179
00:13:50,224 --> 00:13:55,685
And I can easily tear down one
or two doors with my new powers!

180
00:13:55,763 --> 00:13:57,196
- Naruto!
- Naruto!

181
00:13:59,567 --> 00:14:00,795
Old Lady Tsunade...

182
00:14:01,769 --> 00:14:02,929
Oh! Watch out!

183
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:17,848
W-Wow...

184
00:15:13,541 --> 00:15:15,600
Listen Konohamaru.

185
00:15:15,810 --> 00:15:18,108
The Hidden Leaf Village is
in great trouble right now!

186
00:15:18,579 --> 00:15:23,482
Our forces have dropped to almost half,
and we have to finish our missions!

187
00:15:25,219 --> 00:15:28,245
That's what I taught you!

188
00:15:30,191 --> 00:15:33,285
Yeah... um... well...

189
00:15:33,428 --> 00:15:34,986
But if we don't accomplish
our missions,

190
00:15:35,063 --> 00:15:39,261
that's letting other countries know
that the village has been weakened.

191
00:15:39,767 --> 00:15:42,292
That's what Iruka Sensei taught you!

192
00:15:50,445 --> 00:15:52,470
Do you not like Old Lady Tsunade?

193
00:15:52,580 --> 00:15:54,946
It's not that!
It's not that at all.

194
00:15:55,716 --> 00:15:56,944
Then what is it?

195
00:15:57,685 --> 00:16:01,348
Soon, nobody will call me
honorable grandson.

196
00:16:02,123 --> 00:16:04,091
Then I'll just become
plain old Konohamaru.

197
00:16:05,493 --> 00:16:07,688
So what's wrong with
plain old Konohamaru?

198
00:16:07,762 --> 00:16:08,524
No...

199
00:16:09,197 --> 00:16:14,032
Why, why?! You hated
being called honorable grandson!

200
00:16:16,737 --> 00:16:19,433
Everybody's going to forget
about the Old Man.

201
00:16:21,442 --> 00:16:22,409
The Old Man.

202
00:16:23,544 --> 00:16:25,978
They're going to forget what
a great Ninja he was,

203
00:16:26,047 --> 00:16:28,413
they're just going to put him away
like an old ashtray.

204
00:16:30,084 --> 00:16:33,952
The new Hokage will make all kinds
of changes in the Leaf Village.

205
00:16:34,555 --> 00:16:36,250
That's not true!

206
00:16:36,390 --> 00:16:38,017
The Hidden Leaf Village is
the Hidden Leaf Village.

207
00:16:38,126 --> 00:16:41,618
And besides,
nobody will forget about the Old Man!

208
00:16:41,963 --> 00:16:44,523
No! They will never forget about him!

209
00:16:45,199 --> 00:16:47,633
They will forget, I guarantee it.

210
00:16:48,069 --> 00:16:49,093
They won't forget!

211
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:50,068
That's a lie!

212
00:16:50,138 --> 00:16:53,539
It's not a lie!
You can't believe what I am saying?!

213
00:16:53,908 --> 00:16:54,840
That's right, I can't!

214
00:16:54,909 --> 00:16:57,070
Oh boy!

215
00:16:57,778 --> 00:16:59,075
Come with me, Konohamaru!

216
00:16:59,814 --> 00:17:02,044
We just have to get Old Lady Tsunade
to promise

217
00:17:02,116 --> 00:17:04,641
that she won't change
the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

218
00:17:04,852 --> 00:17:05,784
And then on top of that,

219
00:17:05,853 --> 00:17:08,981
we can get everybody to promise us
that they won't forget about the Old Man!

220
00:17:09,157 --> 00:17:09,885
What?

221
00:17:10,725 --> 00:17:12,249
Isn't that what you want?

222
00:17:18,866 --> 00:17:22,563
<i>I can't believe that I let</i>
<i>Lady Tsunade out of my sight!</i>

223
00:17:29,677 --> 00:17:31,144
Did you find her, Tonton?

224
00:17:45,793 --> 00:17:49,024
Revitalizing the cells, I see.

225
00:17:57,371 --> 00:17:59,532
I've found you Lady Tsunade.

226
00:17:59,774 --> 00:18:00,468
What?

227
00:18:04,845 --> 00:18:07,211
Lady Tsunade is studying

228
00:18:08,382 --> 00:18:10,942
Be quiet! I can't concentrate.

229
00:18:12,753 --> 00:18:13,981
Concentrate?!

230
00:18:14,388 --> 00:18:17,016
I've never heard you use that word
except when you're gambling.

231
00:18:18,426 --> 00:18:20,291
Is that Shizune's voice?

232
00:18:20,828 --> 00:18:22,261
Shizune...

233
00:18:25,199 --> 00:18:28,225
Do you remember that Medical Ninja
by the name of Kabuto?

234
00:18:29,437 --> 00:18:30,267
What about him?

235
00:18:30,538 --> 00:18:34,065
His ability to create new cells.

236
00:18:34,642 --> 00:18:37,509
I was researching ways to use
that power on the patients.

237
00:18:38,846 --> 00:18:40,336
For Lee?

238
00:18:40,982 --> 00:18:47,285
If the 50% chance becomes 51%,
it's worth a try.

239
00:18:47,655 --> 00:18:51,489
It really depends on the individual's traits.

240
00:18:52,493 --> 00:18:55,519
Even for you,
it might be hard to acquire those powers.

241
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:00,790
I'll just have to try.

242
00:19:02,803 --> 00:19:05,271
I am the Fifth Hokage, after all.

243
00:19:14,615 --> 00:19:17,277
It can't be helped, Konohamaru.

244
00:19:17,985 --> 00:19:20,317
I am the Third Hokage, after all.

245
00:19:21,088 --> 00:19:24,023
If you don't like it,
you should just quit!

246
00:19:24,992 --> 00:19:27,460
Everybody from the village
is my family.

247
00:19:27,962 --> 00:19:31,625
To protect the family,
that is the duty of a Hokage.

248
00:19:34,101 --> 00:19:35,932
Oh! Old Man!

249
00:19:50,851 --> 00:19:53,285
Just for today,
I'm making a special exception.

250
00:19:57,925 --> 00:19:59,654
What's the matter Konohamaru?

251
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:02,192
Don't you want to see
Old Lady Tsunade?

252
00:20:02,596 --> 00:20:03,290
No.

253
00:20:12,406 --> 00:20:16,274
<i>I'll just have to do it.</i>
<i>I am the Fifth Hokage, after all.</i>

254
00:20:17,345 --> 00:20:22,214
<i>It can't be helped, Konohamaru.</i>
<i>I am the Third Hokage, after all.</i>

255
00:20:23,851 --> 00:20:27,787
It can't be helped.
I am the honorable grandson, after all.

256
00:20:28,222 --> 00:20:29,052
Huh?

257
00:20:29,423 --> 00:20:33,189
I am Konohamaru of
the Hidden Leaf Village, after all!

258
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:36,752
H-Hey Konohamaru, wait!

259
00:20:37,164 --> 00:20:41,066
What's going on with him?
Hey Konohamaru!

260
00:20:47,441 --> 00:20:48,408
Lady Tsunade?

261
00:20:48,843 --> 00:20:49,571
Nothing...

262
00:21:06,694 --> 00:21:11,393
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

263
00:21:11,465 --> 00:21:15,799
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

264
00:21:16,404 --> 00:21:19,931
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

265
00:21:21,175 --> 00:21:25,635
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

266
00:21:25,813 --> 00:21:31,251
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

267
00:21:31,752 --> 00:21:36,052
<i>That hold us together</i>

268
00:21:36,524 --> 00:21:45,762
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

269
00:21:45,833 --> 00:21:48,427
<i>you say laughingly</i>

270
00:21:48,669 --> 00:21:54,335
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

271
00:21:54,909 --> 00:21:59,278
<i>Like a comet,</i>

272
00:21:59,347 --> 00:22:05,445
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

273
00:22:05,519 --> 00:22:12,618
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

274
00:22:13,627 --> 00:22:23,002
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

275
00:22:24,338 --> 00:22:31,870
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

276
00:22:31,946 --> 00:22:35,939
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

277
00:22:38,719 --> 00:22:40,778
Back then, Sensei taught me

278
00:22:40,855 --> 00:22:44,689
that I would grow up to become
a great Ninja

279
00:22:44,759 --> 00:22:47,853
through lots of effort and
competition with my rivals.

280
00:22:48,262 --> 00:22:49,889
His words put me at ease.

281
00:22:50,131 --> 00:22:53,567
A path opened up for me
just when I was unsure of myself.

282
00:22:54,168 --> 00:22:56,830
I realized that all I had to do
was try my best.

283
00:22:57,438 --> 00:22:58,370
But now...

284
00:22:58,539 --> 00:23:02,873
Next time: "Sensei and Student:
The Bond of the Shinobi"
